## 💡 상태 머신 (State Machine) 설계

### 상태 다이어그램

```
STABLE ──warning──> WARNING
  ▲                  │
  │                overload
  │                  ▼
  └──recovery──  OVERLOAD
                  │
                  └─ temp>90 → SHUTDOWN
```

### 상태 머신 구현

```rust
enum SystemState {
    STABLE,
    WARNING,
    OVERLOAD,
    SHUTDOWN,
}

fn handle_event(state: SystemState, event: &str) -> SystemState {
    match (state, event) {
        (SystemState::STABLE, "warning") => SystemState::WARNING,
        (SystemState::STABLE, _) => SystemState::STABLE,

        (SystemState::WARNING, "overload") => SystemState::OVERLOAD,
        (SystemState::WARNING, "recover") => SystemState::STABLE,
        (SystemState::WARNING, _) => SystemState::WARNING,

        (SystemState::OVERLOAD, "critical") => SystemState::SHUTDOWN,
        (SystemState::OVERLOAD, "cool") => SystemState::WARNING,
        (SystemState::OVERLOAD, _) => SystemState::OVERLOAD,

        (SystemState::SHUTDOWN, "restart") => SystemState::STABLE,
        (SystemState::SHUTDOWN, _) => SystemState::SHUTDOWN,
    }
}
```

